{"tid":1870173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣公司一啲危機意識都冇","createTime":"2020-02-08T15:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T15:45:18.000Z","uid":348608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"50c0cacf14285aab82f1f950e4b1e746441340d1","tid":1870173,"uid":348608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"之前公司都話有安排緊輪班 諗住佢都有返啲良心<br />\n點知前排新港中心有單確診左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公司係港威都近 大家都好鬼驚 諗住應該home office喇掛<br />\n點知話一切如常 淨係話會調走某啲人<br />\n講真 你調走果少少人其實有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公司冇彈性工作時間 冇午餐津貼 又冇遙距工作措施 <br />\n就算有 都吾係個個都可以用到<br />\n好多同事仲係要冒住受感染既風險返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前同行中信銀行既做法已經令好多人吾滿意啦<br />\n真係一啲危機意識都冇 我地都好無奈<br />\n高層話運動多啲 放假冇咩事吾好出街 平日就吾好出街食 聽到我地R晒頭<br />\n我都知依家仲有好多公司都會將營利凌駕於員工健康之上既<br />\n搞到依家個個返工都心驚膽跳<br />\n係度唯有祝打工仔好運啦#$$$#<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0d74edb1ecf5096bd4ce902021b7a4fda09bca","tid":1870173,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOo%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=770c13f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"}]}